name: Bounded context (group)
category: Architecture
tags: [ddd, microservices, boundary, worker]
description: Wrap related services with a boundary node — useful for DDD or microservices service-area diagrams.
---
# Bounded context with explicit boundary

nodes:
  - id: box, kind: boundary, label: "orders bounded context", x: 60, y: 30, w: 540, h: 250
  - id: api, kind: service,  label: "Orders API",  x: 90,  y: 70,  w: 150, h: 80
  - id: wkr, kind: worker,   label: Worker,        x: 90,  y: 180, w: 150, h: 80
  - id: q,   kind: queue,    label: "Internal Q",  x: 270, y: 125, w: 150, h: 80
  - id: db,  kind: store,    label: "Orders DB",   x: 450, y: 125, w: 130, h: 80

edges:
  - api  -> q
  - q   ..> wkr
  - wkr  -> db
  - api ..> db, label: "read"
